name: Untitled_000
description:
The UNTITLED series are special limited edition outputs from on-going research. They capture a moment in a process. There will only always be 5/5 with the occasional 1/1. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs.
